## Bootstrap your day ##
Bootstrap your day!

* Overview of calendar events today
* Tasks today (Evernote, Todoist, Google Calendar)
* Flights?
* Traffic information (google-directions)
* Learn a new word each day! (Babel?, dict.cc?)
* Edit the card description.

